{"tid":517532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時隔兩年　「Pokemon Go」終獲批登陸中國","createTime":"2018-01-02T11:44:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T16:21:25.000Z","uid":20933,"like":2,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5892740139a783727deb1a4bb77a42e4518437cd","tid":517532,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"在2016年7月起一度風靡全港，令大街小巷人人都拿着手機捉精靈「Pokemon Go」，終於獲內地官方批准，合法登陸。開發商Niantic宣布，與中國網絡公司網易合作，網易將幫助Niantic適應中國的互聯網監管規定。公司創辦人漢克（John Hanke）指：「絕對希望將當前的遊戲推到中國市場。除此以為，我們還有機會在中國，為中國和全球市場開發遊戲。」<br />\n <br />\n《金融時報》報道，「Pokemon Go」在2016年發行時，曾掀起全球熱潮，數億玩家下載遊戲，然而到了同年年終，熱潮冷卻，一大堆玩家退出遊戲，獨剩「穩定」的玩家團體。Niantic繼續完善遊戲，推出更多新功能，包括現實世界的天氣將影響遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n漢克表示，2016年遊戲面世令業績大漲，雖然2017年的收入不及2016年，但同樣強勁。"},{"pid":"7536263111424fd847bd3b55372ecde511b48163","tid":517532,"uid":54593,"like":85,"dislike":3,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"隻game得返廢中廢老玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da85ba6d8b02ac1a1dccd7c5ed5e2bc7fb7fb5f3","tid":517532,"uid":116530,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:46:59.000Z","msg":"精靈寶可夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af4a03cf58af25d204fa3a9dba076b7594af2f9","tid":517532,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:48:03.000Z","msg":"仲有人玩？"},{"pid":"404e553f0737fc2fd334e4adcaaa89d49cfe9d95","tid":517532,"uid":91931,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"仲撚有人玩咩"},{"pid":"f7cfeb19dd1cacd26ebf8d8766aef48349d7a3d7","tid":517532,"uid":67353,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T11:50:06.000Z","msg":"諗起Pokemon go 篇文<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國人玩到 其他地方都冇咩人玩啦"},{"pid":"765b66fc5122952fc8e4984df37f62cd61e7e422","tid":517532,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike